    <item>
      <title>如果美国撤资法案成为法律，TikTok 计划全面法律斗争</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-12/tiktok-plans-full-legal-fight-if-us-divestment-bill-becomes-law</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，如果针对该应用程序的美国最新立法成为法律，TikTok 打算在考虑从中国母公司字节跳动有限公司进行任何形式的剥离之前，先排除所有法律挑战。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-12/tiktok-plans-full-legal-fight-if-us-divestment-bill-becomes-law</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 12 Mar 2024 18:30:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Chamath Palihapitiya 的风险投资公司解雇了两名合伙人，聘请了律师事务所</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-12/palihapitiya-vc-firm-fires-two-partners-hires-law-firm</link>
      <description><![CDATA[根据彭博社审阅的一封致投资者的信函，由播客兼 Facebook 前高管查马斯·帕里哈皮蒂亚 (Chamath Palihapitiya) 领导的风险投资公司 Social Capital 以未公开的“情况”为由解雇了两名合伙人。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-12/palihapitiya-vc-firm-fires-two-partners-hires-law-firm</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 12 Mar 2024 18:07:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>众议院即将进行撤资投票，TikTok 聚焦参议院</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-12/tiktok-focuses-on-senate-as-house-barrels-toward-divestment-vote</link>
      <description><![CDATA[TikTok 首席执行官 Shou Chew 周二前往国会山游说反对一项法案，该法案将迫使该应用程序的中国母公司出售该应用程序，否则将在美国面临禁令。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-12/tiktok-focuses-on-senate-as-house-barrels-toward-divestment-vote</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 12 Mar 2024 17:57:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英伟达引领半导体股在两天抛售后反弹</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-12/nvidia-leads-semiconductor-stock-rebound-after-two-day-selloff</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周二，在半导体指数遭遇两个多月来最严重的两日跌幅后，英伟达公司(Nvidia Corp.)带领芯片制造商股票走高。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-12/nvidia-leads-semiconductor-stock-rebound-after-two-day-selloff</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 12 Mar 2024 17:50:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>意大利希望半导体公司获得更大的投资份额</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-12/italy-wants-bigger-share-of-investments-by-semiconductors-firm</link>
      <description><![CDATA[乔治亚·梅洛尼 (Giorgia Meloni) 政府要求芯片制造商意法半导体 (STMicroelectronics NV) 向意大利提供更大比例的投资，这是意大利与法国商业关系紧张的最新迹象。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-12/italy-wants-bigger-share-of-investments-by-semiconductors-firm</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 12 Mar 2024 16:47:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>GBTC 亏损数十亿美元后，灰度计划成立新的比特币基金</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-12/grayscale-plans-mini-gbtc-launch-as-fund-sheds-billions</link>
      <description><![CDATA[灰度投资有限责任公司 (Grayscale Investments LLC) 打算推出世界上最大的比特币基金的克隆品，因为该基金因成本较低的竞争对手而损失了数十亿美元。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-12/grayscale-plans-mini-gbtc-launch-as-fund-sheds-billions</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 12 Mar 2024 12:33:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Rackspace Technology 即将与债权人达成重组协议</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-11/apollo-s-rackspace-nears-deal-for-debt-restructuring-new-loan</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，Rackspace Technology Inc. 即将与债权人达成重组协议，该协议将向其提供新现金、减少债务并重新调整债权人还款额度。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-11/apollo-s-rackspace-nears-deal-for-debt-restructuring-new-loan</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 11 Mar 2024 22:00:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
